item.title: CVE-2019-0274|2024-08-04T17:44:16.199Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20mobile%20platform%20sdk
item.description: SAP Mobile Platform SDK allows an attacker to prevent legitimate users from accessing a service, either by crashing or flooding the service (i.e. denial of service). Fixed in versions 3.1 SP03 PL02, SDK 3.1 SP04, or later.
